Regulation (EC) No 1059/2003 is hereby amended as follows:
1. Annex I shall be amended in accordance with the text shown in Annex I to this Regulation;
2. Annex II shall be amended in accordance with the text shown in Annex II to this Regulation;
3. Annex III shall be amended in accordance with the text shown in Annex III to this Regulation.
